1
00:00:22,464 --> 00:00:26,432
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

2
00:00:26,432 --> 00:00:29,728
♪And the dazed confusion♪

3
00:00:30,976 --> 00:00:33,681
♪Should we let go of♪

4
00:00:33,681 --> 00:00:35,904
♪The stubborn madness♪

5
00:00:35,904 --> 00:00:39,072
♪And naive recklessness now♪

6
00:00:40,192 --> 00:00:43,840
♪Those years, those faces♪

7
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:48,763
♪Those old scars we can't erase♪

8
00:00:49,824 --> 00:00:52,460
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

9
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:57,594
♪Piercing the sorrow within♪

10
00:01:08,716 --> 00:01:12,736
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

11
00:01:13,536 --> 00:01:18,076
♪The wounds we've borne
are medals hidden within♪

12
00:01:18,336 --> 00:01:22,391
♪Standing alone on an open plain♪

13
00:01:23,168 --> 00:01:26,851
♪We gaze at the stars♪

14
00:01:31,228 --> 00:01:34,816
=The Dream Maker=

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,784
=Episode 27=

16
00:01:38,418 --> 00:01:39,379
A while back,

17
00:01:39,619 --> 00:01:41,338
you secured an eight-million-yuan loan

18
00:01:41,739 --> 00:01:44,179
in the town government's name
for the industrial park.

19
00:01:44,778 --> 00:01:45,659
Is that true?

20
00:01:46,338 --> 00:01:48,938
Sure. Road is a vital component
of urban infrastructure.

21
00:01:49,778 --> 00:01:50,778
Is there an issue?

22
00:01:51,539 --> 00:01:52,418
The industrial park

23
00:01:52,899 --> 00:01:54,418
was spearheaded by Gao Xuemei,

24
00:01:54,659 --> 00:01:58,099
director of Chunmei Printery
and wife of Xie Chunlai.

25
00:01:58,698 --> 00:02:00,259
So, the town government stepped in

26
00:02:00,619 --> 00:02:02,179
to secure the loan and build the road,

27
00:02:02,498 --> 00:02:06,058
which must surely be related

28
00:02:06,619 --> 00:02:07,578
to Mr. Xie's wife.

29
00:02:07,698 --> 00:02:09,578
Is my understanding correct?

30
00:02:10,379 --> 00:02:13,099
If you mean Ms. Gao,
director of the printery, then yes.

31
00:02:13,418 --> 00:02:15,418
But if you mean Mr. Xie's wife,

32
00:02:15,578 --> 00:02:18,018
then no. Frankly, there's no connection.

33
00:02:23,659 --> 00:02:24,379
Take a look.

34
00:02:25,138 --> 00:02:27,259
Do you recognize this TV set?

35
00:02:28,099 --> 00:02:30,138
Of course.
It belongs to our town government.

36
00:02:30,618 --> 00:02:32,779
Qian Changyuan wanted
to give it to the government,

37
00:02:32,779 --> 00:02:34,858
but we all felt it was too valuable.

38
00:02:35,539 --> 00:02:37,259
So, the town government paid

39
00:02:37,539 --> 00:02:38,939
to buy this TV set.

40
00:02:39,298 --> 00:02:40,184
How much did it cost?

41
00:02:40,458 --> 00:02:41,219
800 yuan.

42
00:02:43,738 --> 00:02:44,779
We've done some surveys.

43
00:02:45,178 --> 00:02:45,898
Take a look.

44
00:02:46,339 --> 00:02:49,099
This imported 18-inch color TV set

45
00:02:49,659 --> 00:02:52,458
cost at least 2,000 yuan back then.

46
00:02:53,059 --> 00:02:53,779
So,

47
00:02:54,379 --> 00:02:56,458
why did Qian Changyuan
only charge you 800?

48
00:02:57,779 --> 00:02:58,379
Really?

49
00:03:00,259 --> 00:03:02,379
But that was the price
Qian Changyuan quoted.

50
00:03:02,499 --> 00:03:03,578
He said it was secondhand.

51
00:03:04,339 --> 00:03:05,018
Ms. Li,

52
00:03:05,499 --> 00:03:07,779
I don't know
if you ever did any market research.

53
00:03:08,219 --> 00:03:11,858
Buying this
two-thousand-yuan color TV set

54
00:03:12,259 --> 00:03:13,539
required a TV purchase coupon.

55
00:03:14,858 --> 00:03:17,458
Even then,
it was hard to buy it on the market.

56
00:03:17,819 --> 00:03:18,939
No secondhand ones at all.

57
00:03:20,539 --> 00:03:21,578
I've already stated

58
00:03:21,819 --> 00:03:24,219
I truly didn't
know the TV set's actual price.

59
00:03:24,819 --> 00:03:26,779
Qian Changyuan is a well-known salesman
in town.

60
00:03:26,979 --> 00:03:28,298
He has many sourcing channels.

61
00:03:28,618 --> 00:03:31,219
So we never questioned his word.

62
00:03:31,779 --> 00:03:32,339
Of course,

63
00:03:32,659 --> 00:03:35,018
if the TV set really cost
what you claimed,

64
00:03:35,219 --> 00:03:37,939
it was indeed our oversight
and work error.

65
00:03:38,898 --> 00:03:40,059
Once I figure out the truth,

66
00:03:40,298 --> 00:03:43,339
the town government
will cover the price difference.

67
00:03:46,499 --> 00:03:48,898
This isn't about the difference.
Don't downplay the issue.

68
00:03:49,738 --> 00:03:51,819
Listen, is this
an under-the-table agreement

69
00:03:52,099 --> 00:03:54,379
between Zheng Decheng
and the self-employed individuals?

70
00:03:54,539 --> 00:03:56,178
And besides the TV set,

71
00:03:57,578 --> 00:03:58,259
any other stuff?

72
00:03:58,618 --> 00:04:00,138
No under-the-table agreements at all.

73
00:04:00,499 --> 00:04:01,259
Li Qiuping,

74
00:04:03,059 --> 00:04:03,898
please be honest.

75
00:04:04,298 --> 00:04:05,499
I've been quite honest.

76
00:04:06,298 --> 00:04:09,018
Mr. Liu Weimin, forgive my bluntness,

77
00:04:09,339 --> 00:04:11,379
but how is
the investigation progressing?

78
00:04:12,018 --> 00:04:13,939
The whole of Yuehai is at a standstill.

79
00:04:14,418 --> 00:04:16,058
Yet you're fixated on a TV set,

80
00:04:16,178 --> 00:04:18,058
relentlessly hounding our government.

81
00:04:18,779 --> 00:04:19,979
If this drags on much longer

82
00:04:20,298 --> 00:04:22,219
and Yuehai's economy suffers,

83
00:04:22,618 --> 00:04:24,298
can you take responsibility for that?

84
00:04:31,899 --> 00:04:34,099
They grilled me
about this TV set for ages.

85
00:04:36,219 --> 00:04:37,208
They asked me too.

86
00:04:39,224 --> 00:04:40,219
They asked everyone.

87
00:04:43,418 --> 00:04:44,579
Who would've thought

88
00:04:45,019 --> 00:04:46,938
one TV set could cause so much trouble?

89
00:04:47,659 --> 00:04:48,699
So what now?

90
00:04:50,178 --> 00:04:51,539
I can't dismantle it.

91
00:04:54,219 --> 00:04:55,539
Maybe

92
00:04:55,539 --> 00:04:57,240
we could sell the TV set?

93
00:04:58,039 --> 00:04:58,659
Good idea.

94
00:05:00,019 --> 00:05:01,738
That would make us look more suspicious.

95
00:05:03,019 --> 00:05:05,139
Forget selling it.
We should just watch it.

96
00:05:05,738 --> 00:05:07,899
We've only ever watched the news.

97
00:05:08,618 --> 00:05:09,118
Right.

98
00:05:41,418 --> 00:05:42,099
Mr. Zheng.

99
00:05:53,378 --> 00:05:54,779
Ms. Li, I'm sorry

100
00:05:54,858 --> 00:05:55,738
to trouble you.

101
00:05:56,099 --> 00:05:58,258
We can't make it clear on the phone.
What happened?

102
00:05:58,339 --> 00:05:58,938
Is it serious?

103
00:05:59,339 --> 00:06:01,738
Dapeng broke Cai Jun's arm,
the son of Director Cai.

104
00:06:01,798 --> 00:06:03,019
He's still hospitalized.

105
00:06:03,339 --> 00:06:04,472
What did Director Cai say?

106
00:06:04,779 --> 00:06:05,699
Gaokao is around,

107
00:06:05,699 --> 00:06:06,858
so Director Cai is furious.

108
00:06:07,099 --> 00:06:09,058
He said
if this affects his son's exam results,

109
00:06:09,219 --> 00:06:10,264
Dapeng won't get off easy.

110
00:06:10,459 --> 00:06:12,258
I pleaded every way I could,

111
00:06:12,418 --> 00:06:13,818
but Director Cai refused to settle.

112
00:06:14,099 --> 00:06:14,899
Decheng isn't here.

113
00:06:15,139 --> 00:06:16,418
I have to ask you for help.

114
00:06:16,579 --> 00:06:18,099
Why did Dapeng fight Cai Jun?

115
00:06:18,618 --> 00:06:20,378
Dapeng is quite stubborn.

116
00:06:20,659 --> 00:06:21,699
He refused to tell me.

117
00:06:23,659 --> 00:06:25,298
Dapeng knows
about Mr. Zheng's situation?

118
00:06:25,618 --> 00:06:26,418
He must know.

119
00:06:27,019 --> 00:06:28,539
News has been spread everywhere.

120
00:06:28,738 --> 00:06:29,779
Where is Dapeng now?

121
00:06:29,899 --> 00:06:30,659
I locked him in.

122
00:06:31,579 --> 00:06:32,339
He's in there.

123
00:06:33,539 --> 00:06:34,258
Right here.

124
00:06:39,818 --> 00:06:40,339
Dapeng!

125
00:06:42,659 --> 00:06:43,219
Dapeng!

126
00:06:43,779 --> 00:06:45,279
Come on. Chase him!

127
00:06:49,339 --> 00:06:49,938
Zheng Dapeng!

128
00:06:51,178 --> 00:06:51,699
Zheng Dapeng!

129
00:06:52,298 --> 00:06:52,798
Zheng...

130
00:06:53,498 --> 00:06:53,998
Stop!

131
00:06:54,858 --> 00:06:55,539
Zheng Dapeng!

132
00:06:55,858 --> 00:06:56,358
Stop.

133
00:06:56,459 --> 00:06:57,019
Stop there!

134
00:06:57,339 --> 00:06:58,818
Let me go!

135
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,938
You caused trouble and ran away?
Is that what your dad taught you?

136
00:07:01,938 --> 00:07:03,938
Why are you bringing my dad into this?

137
00:07:04,058 --> 00:07:05,298
Now you defend your dad?

138
00:07:05,592 --> 00:07:07,258
What were you thinking when you fought?

139
00:07:07,258 --> 00:07:08,579
Do you realize how serious it is?

140
00:07:08,779 --> 00:07:10,459
I'm 18! I'll do whatever I want!

141
00:07:10,459 --> 00:07:11,738
Mind your own business!

142
00:07:11,899 --> 00:07:13,058
So you know you're 18?

143
00:07:13,418 --> 00:07:16,019
As an adult,
take responsibility for your actions.

144
00:07:16,298 --> 00:07:17,496
If you hit someone, apologize.

145
00:07:17,579 --> 00:07:19,178
Don't you
understand such a simple thing?

146
00:07:19,298 --> 00:07:21,258
Do all cadres chatter like you?

147
00:07:26,339 --> 00:07:26,839
Get up.

148
00:07:26,899 --> 00:07:27,979
Come on, get up.

149
00:07:28,088 --> 00:07:28,899
Where are you going?

150
00:07:28,899 --> 00:07:29,539
- Let go!
- Tell me!

151
00:07:29,659 --> 00:07:31,219
Get out of here! I'm not apologizing.

152
00:07:31,779 --> 00:07:33,779
Ma Weidong, I'll talk to Dapeng.

153
00:07:34,058 --> 00:07:34,659
You may leave.

154
00:07:34,738 --> 00:07:36,258
Ms. Li, you don't know him well.

155
00:07:36,258 --> 00:07:36,938
He's sly.

156
00:07:37,219 --> 00:07:39,019
You called me here,
yet you don't trust me?

157
00:07:40,899 --> 00:07:42,258
Fine, I trust you.

158
00:07:42,899 --> 00:07:44,019
You talk to him then.

159
00:07:44,699 --> 00:07:46,219
Behave! I mean it.

160
00:07:48,899 --> 00:07:49,899
Pick up your textbooks.

161
00:07:54,514 --> 00:07:57,938
(A bad father has a bad son)

162
00:07:57,938 --> 00:07:58,659
Who wrote this?

163
00:07:59,099 --> 00:07:59,938
What's it to you?

164
00:08:00,082 --> 00:08:00,920
(Motherless Child)

165
00:08:02,219 --> 00:08:03,938
Why are you so hostile?

166
00:08:06,699 --> 00:08:07,579
You're hurt too.

167
00:08:09,178 --> 00:08:11,099
Tell me what really happened.

168
00:08:11,938 --> 00:08:14,019
What's the point? I still got beaten.

169
00:08:14,418 --> 00:08:15,979
Telling me will help.

170
00:08:24,418 --> 00:08:26,899
Mom, this food tastes awful.

171
00:08:28,498 --> 00:08:29,752
Can you peel an apple for me?

172
00:08:30,339 --> 00:08:31,899
Peel an apple for our son.

173
00:08:31,938 --> 00:08:33,099
Shut it! Forget about apples!

174
00:08:34,258 --> 00:08:34,758
Get up!

175
00:08:35,778 --> 00:08:36,538
Back off!

176
00:08:39,258 --> 00:08:40,498
Finish your meal!

177
00:08:40,579 --> 00:08:42,179
Couldn't win a fight? No apples for you!

178
00:08:42,618 --> 00:08:43,118
Eat!

179
00:08:59,299 --> 00:08:59,858
Come in.

180
00:09:02,618 --> 00:09:03,299
Mr. Cai.

181
00:09:05,419 --> 00:09:06,138
Ms. Li.

182
00:09:08,099 --> 00:09:08,939
Here to apologize?

183
00:09:09,979 --> 00:09:10,479
No need.

184
00:09:11,419 --> 00:09:12,138
I won't accept it.

185
00:09:12,979 --> 00:09:15,419
I've told the school
to deal with this severely.

186
00:09:15,979 --> 00:09:17,179
Gaokao is around.

187
00:09:18,419 --> 00:09:18,919
Look,

188
00:09:19,858 --> 00:09:21,339
my son is beaten up like this.

189
00:09:21,819 --> 00:09:23,059
If he can't take the exam,

190
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,600
Zheng Dapeng won't take it, either.

191
00:09:25,339 --> 00:09:25,898
Exactly.

192
00:09:26,258 --> 00:09:27,498
You'll get expelled.

193
00:09:30,419 --> 00:09:33,378
Mr. Cai, Mrs. Cai,
I think you misunderstood.

194
00:09:34,339 --> 00:09:36,579
I didn't bring Dapeng to apologize.

195
00:09:38,579 --> 00:09:39,658
Then why are you here?

196
00:09:39,939 --> 00:09:41,018
To make Cai Jun apologize.

197
00:09:42,618 --> 00:09:43,459
Are you crazy?

198
00:09:44,138 --> 00:09:46,099
He beat my son!
Why should my son apologize?

199
00:09:46,538 --> 00:09:47,699
What nonsense!

200
00:09:53,579 --> 00:09:54,378
Shut the door.

201
00:09:59,419 --> 00:10:00,658
As Cai Jun's parents,

202
00:10:01,658 --> 00:10:03,579
(A bad father has a bad son)
you recognize his handwriting, right?

203
00:10:04,658 --> 00:10:06,179
Of course, if you don't recognize it,

204
00:10:06,538 --> 00:10:08,059
we can ask his teacher.

205
00:10:08,579 --> 00:10:10,219
Let's see how many insults

206
00:10:10,459 --> 00:10:13,819
on these textbooks were written
by Cai Jun.

207
00:10:14,979 --> 00:10:17,179
Cai Jun has long bullied
and insulted Zheng Dapeng.

208
00:10:17,419 --> 00:10:18,618
He spread lies.

209
00:10:19,179 --> 00:10:21,179
Eventually,
Dapeng reported him to a teacher.

210
00:10:21,618 --> 00:10:22,778
Cai Jun, mad and humiliated,

211
00:10:23,219 --> 00:10:25,419
incited thugs to beat Zheng Dapeng.

212
00:10:25,738 --> 00:10:26,579
What thugs?

213
00:10:27,459 --> 00:10:30,459
Li Qiuping, show me your proof!

214
00:10:30,738 --> 00:10:31,979
You're slandering my son!

215
00:10:33,979 --> 00:10:35,618
Here's testimony from witnesses

216
00:10:35,699 --> 00:10:38,339
(Testimony)
who saw them hitting Zheng Dapeng.

217
00:10:39,018 --> 00:10:41,258
He can confirm the entire event.

218
00:10:42,299 --> 00:10:43,979
Of course, if you don't believe us,

219
00:10:44,299 --> 00:10:46,618
we can go to the police station
right now to file a report.

220
00:10:47,099 --> 00:10:49,699
We can have the witness testify
in front of the police.

221
00:10:52,850 --> 00:10:53,912
(Witness Signature: Zhang Xicai)

222
00:11:02,299 --> 00:11:03,099
Right there.

223
00:11:04,658 --> 00:11:05,378
Beat him!

224
00:11:12,658 --> 00:11:13,158
Buddy.

225
00:11:13,538 --> 00:11:14,378
Pick him up!

226
00:11:18,498 --> 00:11:19,778
What a bold guy!

227
00:11:20,219 --> 00:11:21,498
You told the teacher on me, huh?

228
00:11:25,979 --> 00:11:27,059
Stop looking! Get inside!

229
00:11:27,138 --> 00:11:27,638
Get lost!

230
00:11:32,258 --> 00:11:32,758
My hand!

231
00:11:58,579 --> 00:12:00,419
The police...

232
00:12:00,939 --> 00:12:01,819
No, what police?

233
00:12:02,498 --> 00:12:03,498
File a report?

234
00:12:04,099 --> 00:12:04,599
By the way,

235
00:12:04,898 --> 00:12:06,778
Cai Jun is already 18, right?

236
00:12:10,658 --> 00:12:12,979
Mr. Cai, as an adult,

237
00:12:13,459 --> 00:12:16,258
he should face the consequences
for his actions

238
00:12:16,498 --> 00:12:19,059
and bear the corresponding civil
and criminal liabilities.

239
00:12:19,378 --> 00:12:19,979
Of course,

240
00:12:20,299 --> 00:12:22,538
besides the illegal record
in the public security system,

241
00:12:23,138 --> 00:12:25,699
all of this will also appear
in his permanent record.

242
00:12:26,099 --> 00:12:27,378
It will follow him for life.

243
00:12:27,858 --> 00:12:29,219
A permanent record?

244
00:12:29,738 --> 00:12:30,819
This isn't real, is it?

245
00:12:32,778 --> 00:12:34,419
- Is it true?
- Shut up!

246
00:12:37,979 --> 00:12:38,819
Back off!

247
00:12:44,378 --> 00:12:46,059
Did you write those words in the book?

248
00:12:47,059 --> 00:12:48,498
Did you go find those thugs?

249
00:12:49,339 --> 00:12:50,618
They're not thugs.

250
00:12:50,979 --> 00:12:52,778
They graduated from my school.

251
00:12:54,099 --> 00:12:54,599
Get down!

252
00:12:55,219 --> 00:12:57,778
No need to wear shoes? Barefoot!

253
00:13:03,018 --> 00:13:03,979
Apologize to Dapeng.

254
00:13:06,299 --> 00:13:06,799
Right now!

255
00:13:07,299 --> 00:13:08,419
Or I'll beat you to death!

256
00:13:13,778 --> 00:13:14,299
I'm sorry.

257
00:13:15,979 --> 00:13:16,738
I was wrong.

258
00:13:19,299 --> 00:13:20,179
I won't do it again.

259
00:13:29,339 --> 00:13:30,099
Ms. Li,

260
00:13:30,299 --> 00:13:31,059
well,

261
00:13:31,658 --> 00:13:33,179
he's just a kid, making a mistake.

262
00:13:34,819 --> 00:13:36,498
Since he's already apologized,

263
00:13:38,538 --> 00:13:39,498
let's just let this go.

264
00:13:41,339 --> 00:13:43,898
Mr. Cai, I can't decide.

265
00:13:45,579 --> 00:13:46,579
You make the decision.

266
00:13:47,459 --> 00:13:49,858
Whatever you decide, I'll support you.

267
00:13:56,898 --> 00:13:57,498
Ms. Li,

268
00:13:58,299 --> 00:13:59,618
no, Qiuping,

269
00:13:59,738 --> 00:14:01,018
can I call you Qiuping?

270
00:14:01,699 --> 00:14:04,258
Sure, but that would
make your dad my uncle.

271
00:14:05,459 --> 00:14:06,858
Qiuping, very impressive!

272
00:14:07,579 --> 00:14:08,979
You really learned from my dad.

273
00:14:09,219 --> 00:14:11,099
The way you talk

274
00:14:11,179 --> 00:14:12,138
is like your dad.

275
00:14:13,618 --> 00:14:14,579
So, tell me.

276
00:14:15,138 --> 00:14:17,618
Why did you choose
to forgive Cai Jun in the end?

277
00:14:20,778 --> 00:14:22,059
Well, when his dad hit him,

278
00:14:22,059 --> 00:14:23,459
he looked so pitiful.

279
00:14:23,618 --> 00:14:25,378
But weren't you pitiful too
when he hit you?

280
00:14:26,299 --> 00:14:27,138
Your heart softened?

281
00:14:27,579 --> 00:14:28,618
I don't believe that.

282
00:14:31,018 --> 00:14:33,059
My dad told me not
to push a defeated enemy.

283
00:14:33,738 --> 00:14:35,498
Now, I have leverage over Cai Jun.

284
00:14:36,299 --> 00:14:37,419
He won't mess with me again.

285
00:14:38,179 --> 00:14:39,299
But if I filed a report,

286
00:14:39,419 --> 00:14:40,419
giving him a record,

287
00:14:42,018 --> 00:14:44,018
he might become desperate.

288
00:14:44,498 --> 00:14:46,219
Who knows what trouble
he might cause then?

289
00:14:48,099 --> 00:14:49,138
You're right.

290
00:14:50,858 --> 00:14:53,339
So, problem solved now.

291
00:14:53,658 --> 00:14:54,738
I take you back to school?

292
00:14:55,299 --> 00:14:56,898
No need. School's closed these days.

293
00:14:56,979 --> 00:14:58,219
I'll study for exams at home.

294
00:15:00,258 --> 00:15:00,939
Qiuping,

295
00:15:02,979 --> 00:15:04,059
can I go to Yuehai?

296
00:15:16,618 --> 00:15:18,939
I bought some reference books
and left them on your desk.

297
00:15:19,498 --> 00:15:21,738
If you need anything else,
I can buy it tomorrow.

298
00:15:22,059 --> 00:15:22,939
I don't need anything.

299
00:15:23,219 --> 00:15:24,059
Thanks, Qiuping.

300
00:15:25,258 --> 00:15:27,219
The town cadres have scheduled shifts.

301
00:15:27,378 --> 00:15:29,979
Each person will spare some time
every day to study with you.

302
00:15:30,618 --> 00:15:32,138
If you have any daily needs

303
00:15:32,219 --> 00:15:33,898
or questions about your studies,

304
00:15:34,099 --> 00:15:35,179
you can tell any of them.

305
00:15:35,699 --> 00:15:37,138
I have no problem with studying.

306
00:15:38,819 --> 00:15:40,538
Brag after you get into university.

307
00:15:41,898 --> 00:15:43,419
We're done with the construction fee.

308
00:15:44,099 --> 00:15:44,858
Well,

309
00:15:45,378 --> 00:15:46,419
once we have the money,

310
00:15:47,059 --> 00:15:48,099
we can build the city.

311
00:15:48,979 --> 00:15:49,939
But who'd have thought

312
00:15:50,618 --> 00:15:53,498
building the city
would bring even more trouble?

313
00:15:55,099 --> 00:15:56,819
Mr. Zheng, please stop talking.

314
00:15:57,219 --> 00:15:57,858
We have rules.

315
00:15:58,059 --> 00:16:00,138
During the investigation,
I can't converse with you.

316
00:16:02,059 --> 00:16:03,099
So many rules!

317
00:16:04,498 --> 00:16:05,738
Your answer is correct.

318
00:16:07,459 --> 00:16:09,059
But there's a small issue, Dapeng.

319
00:16:09,378 --> 00:16:10,179
I'm a neat man.

320
00:16:11,579 --> 00:16:13,258
For some reason, I brush my teeth

321
00:16:13,979 --> 00:16:15,179
twice a day.

322
00:16:16,059 --> 00:16:16,559
Sir.

323
00:16:17,138 --> 00:16:20,299
We want to build
a new factory in this area.

324
00:16:20,658 --> 00:16:21,939
This plot is off the table.

325
00:16:21,959 --> 00:16:22,459
We...

326
00:16:22,459 --> 00:16:23,339
Your mom took it!

327
00:16:23,738 --> 00:16:24,979
Keep arguing!

328
00:16:25,018 --> 00:16:25,518
Go on!

329
00:16:25,579 --> 00:16:26,339
Fight!

330
00:16:26,618 --> 00:16:27,219
Go on, fight!

331
00:16:27,538 --> 00:16:28,038
Fight!

332
00:16:28,219 --> 00:16:29,219
- Without...
- Grab your weapons.

333
00:16:29,459 --> 00:16:30,099
Come on, fight!

334
00:16:30,179 --> 00:16:30,898
Use this!

335
00:16:31,339 --> 00:16:32,219
Yes, grab your tools!

336
00:16:32,699 --> 00:16:33,339
Problem solved.

337
00:16:34,099 --> 00:16:35,339
Fight back!

338
00:16:35,819 --> 00:16:36,419
Right?

339
00:16:36,778 --> 00:16:37,278
Right?

340
00:16:38,138 --> 00:16:39,459
I can tell it's serious.

341
00:16:40,898 --> 00:16:42,819
Come on, let me sort this out for you.

342
00:16:43,018 --> 00:16:44,258
Your family

343
00:16:44,378 --> 00:16:46,219
stacked unwanted stuff by the door.

344
00:16:46,419 --> 00:16:46,919
Then,

345
00:16:47,179 --> 00:16:49,299
you think his mom took it away, right?

346
00:16:49,378 --> 00:16:50,339
He's talking nonsense!

347
00:16:50,378 --> 00:16:51,299
Yes, his mom took it!

348
00:16:51,299 --> 00:16:52,099
That's the truth.

349
00:16:52,099 --> 00:16:53,699
I understand your dispute now.

350
00:16:54,179 --> 00:16:55,538
Xie, listen to me.

351
00:16:55,898 --> 00:16:56,579
It's simple.

352
00:16:56,618 --> 00:16:58,059
Don't waste your breath.

353
00:16:58,419 --> 00:17:00,138
I'll call the city inspectors.

354
00:17:00,419 --> 00:17:02,738
They'll supervise the cleanup
at their doors.

355
00:17:02,738 --> 00:17:03,378
Problem solved.

356
00:17:03,939 --> 00:17:06,338
It's a very small thing.
No need for city inspectors!

357
00:17:06,399 --> 00:17:06,899
Xie.

358
00:17:06,899 --> 00:17:07,619
It's a trifle.

359
00:17:07,939 --> 00:17:09,859
Our town government can handle this.

360
00:17:09,979 --> 00:17:11,959
I have my own way of solving problems.

361
00:17:11,979 --> 00:17:12,479
You have to

362
00:17:12,538 --> 00:17:13,899
feed and house city inspectors.

363
00:17:14,058 --> 00:17:15,498
My opinion is simple.

364
00:17:16,018 --> 00:17:16,979
I respect yours.

365
00:17:17,219 --> 00:17:18,098
We'll go back now.

366
00:17:18,098 --> 00:17:19,818
- We've known each other for years.
- We're old neighbors.

367
00:17:19,939 --> 00:17:20,619
You came to me.

368
00:17:20,619 --> 00:17:21,619
We'll go back now.

369
00:17:21,979 --> 00:17:23,498
The government will solve it for you.

370
00:17:24,219 --> 00:17:26,139
This could be a model case.

371
00:17:26,338 --> 00:17:26,838
It's done?

372
00:17:27,058 --> 00:17:28,179
Sure. All settled.

373
00:17:31,498 --> 00:17:32,939
Winning without fighting!

374
00:17:32,979 --> 00:17:33,738
Truly impressive!

375
00:17:34,018 --> 00:17:34,538
Impressive!

376
00:17:35,659 --> 00:17:36,338
No big deal.

377
00:17:36,738 --> 00:17:39,338
Just Tan's usual approach.

378
00:17:39,419 --> 00:17:41,058
Look, he and I were just coordinating.

379
00:17:41,818 --> 00:17:42,778
I figured it out.

380
00:17:43,219 --> 00:17:44,338
My dad, Qiuping,

381
00:17:44,659 --> 00:17:45,778
you three deputy mayors,

382
00:17:46,179 --> 00:17:47,578
plus Meng and Qingtian,

383
00:17:48,179 --> 00:17:49,338
you guys are basically...

384
00:17:49,619 --> 00:17:50,619
What?

385
00:17:52,699 --> 00:17:54,139
The seven heroes of Yuehai!

386
00:18:16,419 --> 00:18:17,459
Sir, you're awake?

387
00:18:17,699 --> 00:18:18,498
You're all here.

388
00:18:19,098 --> 00:18:19,738
Just arrived.

389
00:18:19,738 --> 00:18:20,778
I overslept.

390
00:18:23,899 --> 00:18:24,459
Right now,

391
00:18:25,219 --> 00:18:27,578
let's summarize our findings.

392
00:18:27,778 --> 00:18:28,278
Okay.

393
00:18:28,558 --> 00:18:29,058
Come on.

394
00:18:29,058 --> 00:18:29,558
Alright.

395
00:18:30,219 --> 00:18:30,939
- Here.
- Here.

396
00:18:34,659 --> 00:18:35,619
According to...

397
00:18:38,979 --> 00:18:41,139
According to Ma Weidong...

398
00:18:41,498 --> 00:18:43,619
Anyone hungry? Come grab some.

399
00:18:43,619 --> 00:18:44,778
- Come on.
- Take one.

400
00:18:44,899 --> 00:18:45,816
You skipped breakfast.

401
00:18:46,179 --> 00:18:48,018
According to Ma Weidong,

402
00:18:49,258 --> 00:18:50,258
Zheng Decheng

403
00:18:50,298 --> 00:18:52,979
sends him money immediately
after getting paid each month.

404
00:18:53,338 --> 00:18:56,699
Part of that money
repays an old debt from turtle farming.

405
00:18:57,139 --> 00:18:59,979
The rest is his son's living expenses.

406
00:19:00,899 --> 00:19:01,859
Other than that,

407
00:19:02,139 --> 00:19:03,480
(Ma Weidong's testimony)
there are no other financial dealings

408
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,578
between them.

409
00:19:05,778 --> 00:19:07,179
What did you find out?

410
00:19:09,379 --> 00:19:11,338
Any findings from the residents?

411
00:19:14,538 --> 00:19:15,038
What?

412
00:19:16,659 --> 00:19:17,778
Just say what you found.

413
00:19:18,498 --> 00:19:19,338
Well, sir,

414
00:19:19,659 --> 00:19:21,018
we split into four teams.

415
00:19:21,419 --> 00:19:23,379
We randomly interviewed workers
on Binhai Road,

416
00:19:23,659 --> 00:19:26,018
residents in the shantytown,
villagers from Yang Village,

417
00:19:26,419 --> 00:19:28,419
and migrant workers from other places.

418
00:19:28,859 --> 00:19:30,578
It's 424 people in total.

419
00:19:31,338 --> 00:19:33,058
They specifically
mentioned the government

420
00:19:33,179 --> 00:19:34,859
providing shelter
for them during typhoons,

421
00:19:35,258 --> 00:19:37,979
securing technical job quotas for them,

422
00:19:38,338 --> 00:19:40,419
and participating in sanitation efforts.

423
00:19:40,979 --> 00:19:42,219
During the Half-Month Talks,

424
00:19:42,338 --> 00:19:43,619
the people especially emphasized

425
00:19:43,778 --> 00:19:45,738
that Zheng Decheng
listened to their opinions.

426
00:19:46,578 --> 00:19:47,659
So, you're saying

427
00:19:48,738 --> 00:19:50,538
that among the people you interviewed,

428
00:19:52,018 --> 00:19:53,738
no one spoke ill of Zheng Decheng?

429
00:19:54,298 --> 00:19:54,798
Yes.

430
00:19:55,139 --> 00:19:57,899
Not only were there no complaints,
but everyone expressed gratitude.

431
00:19:58,419 --> 00:19:59,098
Sir, look,

432
00:19:59,498 --> 00:20:01,498
this is our compiled interview record.

433
00:20:03,954 --> 00:20:06,098
(Interview transcript)

434
00:20:12,818 --> 00:20:14,939
In all my years
doing investigative work,

435
00:20:16,699 --> 00:20:21,338
I've seen spouses turn against each other
and brothers become enemies.

436
00:20:21,979 --> 00:20:24,939
I've even seen fathers
and sons distrust each other,

437
00:20:25,859 --> 00:20:27,738
let alone colleagues in the same office,

438
00:20:27,979 --> 00:20:29,939
who share neither kinship nor ties.

439
00:20:31,098 --> 00:20:33,459
But Yuehai is indeed special.

440
00:20:34,459 --> 00:20:36,939
While Zheng Decheng was
under investigation,

441
00:20:37,578 --> 00:20:40,379
all officials, including the deputy,

442
00:20:41,179 --> 00:20:42,179
spoke up for him.

443
00:20:45,818 --> 00:20:47,058
Sir, what should we do next?

444
00:20:49,578 --> 00:20:51,699
Compile the findings faithfully,

445
00:20:51,979 --> 00:20:53,578
and then report them to the above.

446
00:20:54,119 --> 00:20:54,619
Go for it!

447
00:20:54,619 --> 00:20:55,459
(Pingchuan County First High School)
Do what you can first!

448
00:20:55,639 --> 00:20:56,139
Go for it!

449
00:20:56,139 --> 00:20:56,979
- Take it easy!
- Do the easy ones first!

450
00:20:56,979 --> 00:20:57,338
Okay.

451
00:20:57,338 --> 00:20:57,939
- Come on!
- Don't be nervous.

452
00:20:57,939 --> 00:20:58,498
Come on.

453
00:20:58,578 --> 00:20:59,379
Make way.

454
00:20:59,419 --> 00:21:00,258
Go for it!

455
00:21:04,098 --> 00:21:04,598
Here.

456
00:21:05,098 --> 00:21:05,598
Dapeng.

457
00:21:07,098 --> 00:21:07,818
Get some energy.

458
00:21:10,258 --> 00:21:12,098
You have your exam permit, right?

459
00:21:12,879 --> 00:21:13,379
I forgot it.

460
00:21:13,379 --> 00:21:14,699
What? Pencil and eraser?

461
00:21:15,058 --> 00:21:15,979
Relax, I was kidding.

462
00:21:15,979 --> 00:21:17,498
I'm going in. Too late to confirm now.

463
00:21:18,859 --> 00:21:20,939
Trying to scare me, you rascal.

464
00:21:24,058 --> 00:21:26,018
Dapeng, remember what I told you.

465
00:21:26,659 --> 00:21:28,179
May you know all the correct answers.

466
00:21:30,619 --> 00:21:31,119
I'm leaving.

467
00:21:31,219 --> 00:21:31,719
No drink?

468
00:21:32,018 --> 00:21:32,518
No.

469
00:21:32,659 --> 00:21:33,258
See you later.

470
00:21:33,778 --> 00:21:35,578
Go for it! Be careful!

471
00:21:40,179 --> 00:21:40,939
You can enter now.

472
00:21:46,139 --> 00:21:47,058
Sir, do me a favor.

473
00:21:50,298 --> 00:21:50,899
Dapeng.

474
00:21:52,690 --> 00:21:55,160
(Wish Zheng Dapeng Immediate Success)

475
00:21:57,592 --> 00:22:04,536
(Tan Guangming, Meng Xiaoli, Yu Qingtian,
Li Qiuping, Xie Chunlai, Lin Dongfu, Zheng, Ma Weidong)

476
00:22:08,179 --> 00:22:08,899
Go for it!

477
00:22:10,659 --> 00:22:11,338
Go for it!

478
00:22:26,338 --> 00:22:28,139
Hello, this is Yuehai Town.

479
00:22:28,778 --> 00:22:29,778
Hello, Ms. Li.

480
00:22:30,939 --> 00:22:31,619
Mr. Zhao.

481
00:22:32,139 --> 00:22:34,338
I'm calling to tell you something.

482
00:22:35,659 --> 00:22:38,419
Frankly, I'm a bit guilty of liberalism.

483
00:22:38,939 --> 00:22:41,859
The investigation
into Zheng Decheng is basically over.

484
00:22:42,338 --> 00:22:44,258
The investigation materials
have been submitted,

485
00:22:44,538 --> 00:22:45,659
just for the record.

486
00:22:46,699 --> 00:22:48,219
Okay, I got it, Mr. Zhao.

487
00:22:48,578 --> 00:22:49,859
Here's one more thing.

488
00:22:50,459 --> 00:22:52,219
I'm being transferred to Nanzhou.

489
00:22:53,578 --> 00:22:55,219
Congratulations on your promotion.

490
00:22:55,738 --> 00:22:57,179
You keep working hard

491
00:22:57,419 --> 00:22:58,778
in Yuehai.

492
00:23:00,018 --> 00:23:00,859
Well,

493
00:23:01,419 --> 00:23:03,098
when Zheng Decheng returns,

494
00:23:03,179 --> 00:23:05,619
please pass a message to him for me.

495
00:23:06,699 --> 00:23:07,219
Tell him

496
00:23:07,699 --> 00:23:10,538
to think twice before acting.

497
00:23:10,899 --> 00:23:12,498
Discuss things more between yourselves,

498
00:23:13,338 --> 00:23:14,058
and consult Xia.

499
00:23:14,538 --> 00:23:16,818
I've already advised Xia too.

500
00:23:17,098 --> 00:23:19,139
I see. Don't worry, Mr. Zhao.

501
00:23:19,459 --> 00:23:20,219
I know

502
00:23:20,738 --> 00:23:23,459
you've been under tremendous pressure.

503
00:23:23,818 --> 00:23:26,459
But encountering storms
on the path of development is normal.

504
00:23:26,899 --> 00:23:30,139
As long as you don't lose your way,
there's light at the end of the tunnel.

505
00:23:31,419 --> 00:23:32,219
Don't worry.

506
00:23:32,578 --> 00:23:34,258
Whether Mr. Zheng or me,

507
00:23:34,419 --> 00:23:36,058
or anyone else in our town government,

508
00:23:36,338 --> 00:23:38,899
we'll remember our original aspirations
and not let you down.

509
00:23:39,219 --> 00:23:39,738
Good.

510
00:23:40,619 --> 00:23:42,379
Then, keep in touch!

511
00:23:43,058 --> 00:23:44,399
Goodbye, Mr. Zhao.

512
00:23:44,939 --> 00:23:45,778
Keep in touch!

513
00:23:50,538 --> 00:23:51,139
Ms. Li,

514
00:23:52,179 --> 00:23:53,659
you look so happy. What happened?

515
00:23:54,058 --> 00:23:54,659
Good news.

516
00:23:56,258 --> 00:23:57,699
The storm has passed.

517
00:24:15,018 --> 00:24:15,640
You're awake.

518
00:24:18,379 --> 00:24:19,498
Weimin, you're here.

519
00:24:20,699 --> 00:24:21,738
Continue the questioning?

520
00:24:22,538 --> 00:24:24,699
That's great! I'll go wash my face.

521
00:24:26,219 --> 00:24:27,338
Sorry, I can't feel my leg.

522
00:24:34,979 --> 00:24:35,778
Zheng Decheng.

523
00:24:36,818 --> 00:24:38,139
The investigation is over.

524
00:24:40,659 --> 00:24:41,298
You may go.

525
00:24:46,419 --> 00:24:48,018
The investigation is over?

526
00:24:49,538 --> 00:24:50,139
It's done?

527
00:24:53,778 --> 00:24:54,939
Shall we investigate further?

528
00:24:58,818 --> 00:25:01,619
(The investigation into Zheng Decheng
has finally concluded.)

529
00:25:02,818 --> 00:25:04,139
(The investigation results show)

530
00:25:04,338 --> 00:25:06,899
(Zheng Decheng
had no economic misconduct.)

531
00:25:07,818 --> 00:25:10,899
(Comrades from the DIC
explained the reasons and details)

532
00:25:11,179 --> 00:25:13,338
(to Zheng Decheng in full.)

533
00:25:14,399 --> 00:25:16,179
(The higher-ups)

534
00:25:16,338 --> 00:25:20,179
(recognized Zheng Decheng's work
and Yuehai's development achievements.)

535
00:25:21,619 --> 00:25:22,899
(Amidst Reform and Opening-up,)

536
00:25:23,659 --> 00:25:25,778
(the nation has repealed
outdated regulations,)

537
00:25:26,699 --> 00:25:30,098
(ushering in the separation
of land ownership and use rights.)

538
00:25:31,179 --> 00:25:33,720
- (seven-up, eight-down became history.)
- Can I try that?

539
00:25:35,442 --> 00:25:35,979
Sure.

540
00:25:35,979 --> 00:25:38,338
(It's a fresh start.)

541
00:25:39,258 --> 00:25:40,098
(From then on,)

542
00:25:40,818 --> 00:25:42,859
(we all truly felt)

543
00:25:43,419 --> 00:25:46,419
(the wings
of development were fully unleashed.)

544
00:25:47,766 --> 00:25:52,741
♪Memories won't let me go♪

545
00:25:54,305 --> 00:25:58,265
♪You're the gentle passage of a book♪

546
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:02,134
♪Sweeping me away like a gust of wind♪

547
00:26:03,001 --> 00:26:06,732
♪Like a dream
leaving only loneliness upon waking♪

548
00:26:06,732 --> 00:26:11,000
♪I remember you came♪

549
00:26:11,379 --> 00:26:12,179
Enjoy your meal.

