00:26:19,939 --> 00:26:22,018
The investigators offered me food,

551
00:26:23,064 --> 00:26:24,088
but the food was bland.

552
00:26:25,219 --> 00:26:26,498
The restaurant serves good food.

553
00:26:28,738 --> 00:26:30,139
You waited for me this early

554
00:26:31,498 --> 00:26:33,018
just to treat me to a meal?

555
00:26:36,459 --> 00:26:37,738
Because of my article,

556
00:26:38,139 --> 00:26:39,939
you have been investigated for so long.

557
00:26:40,659 --> 00:26:41,338
Sorry about that.

558
00:26:47,459 --> 00:26:49,179
This drink is my apology.

559
00:26:49,818 --> 00:26:52,152
To you and to Yuehai.

560
00:27:04,024 --> 00:27:05,498
I wrote the article,

561
00:27:06,538 --> 00:27:07,738
but that wasn't my intention.

562
00:27:08,459 --> 00:27:09,578
I needed that article.

563
00:27:11,338 --> 00:27:13,659
Whatever your motive for writing it,

564
00:27:15,939 --> 00:27:17,538
it caused an investigation into me.

565
00:27:19,738 --> 00:27:21,778
It gave me rare quiet time,

566
00:27:22,179 --> 00:27:23,619
so I no longer charged ahead blindly

567
00:27:24,738 --> 00:27:26,058
like before.

568
00:27:27,098 --> 00:27:29,018
I could reflect on the past

569
00:27:29,538 --> 00:27:31,139
and examine my flaws.

570
00:27:32,098 --> 00:27:34,018
I have many shortcomings

571
00:27:34,738 --> 00:27:35,818
and even more to improve.

572
00:27:37,498 --> 00:27:37,998
Anyway,

573
00:27:39,379 --> 00:27:39,879
thank you

574
00:27:40,578 --> 00:27:41,738
for giving me thinking time.

575
00:27:47,939 --> 00:27:48,778
I have a question.

576
00:27:50,179 --> 00:27:51,018
You mentioned

577
00:27:52,219 --> 00:27:54,018
you didn't write about me personally.

578
00:27:55,179 --> 00:27:56,419
But you needed the article.

579
00:27:57,179 --> 00:27:57,738
Why?

580
00:28:00,139 --> 00:28:01,219
I'll work in Shanghai.

581
00:28:11,578 --> 00:28:12,139
I see.

582
00:28:14,459 --> 00:28:15,979
You used Yuehai

583
00:28:16,859 --> 00:28:18,459
as a stepping stone for your career.

584
00:28:20,179 --> 00:28:21,459
You're despicable!

585
00:28:23,419 --> 00:28:25,538
Yes, I'm despicable.

586
00:28:27,419 --> 00:28:29,219
But if you hadn't
blocked my first article,

587
00:28:30,219 --> 00:28:31,419
I wouldn't have done this.

588
00:28:32,578 --> 00:28:33,659
We're even now.

589
00:28:34,058 --> 00:28:35,018
Even?

590
00:28:37,498 --> 00:28:39,058
Don't make excuses!

591
00:28:39,619 --> 00:28:42,258
True, I refused your stamp then.

592
00:28:42,979 --> 00:28:44,498
That was my personal debt.

593
00:28:45,139 --> 00:28:46,619
Not Yuehai's debt to you.

594
00:28:47,538 --> 00:28:49,419
You think you only hurt me?

595
00:28:49,899 --> 00:28:51,818
You hurt every resident of Yuehai!

596
00:28:52,459 --> 00:28:53,379
You knew

597
00:28:54,219 --> 00:28:55,818
what we sacrificed to build a city.

598
00:28:56,538 --> 00:28:57,419
You also knew

599
00:28:57,939 --> 00:28:59,338
how hard people struggled

600
00:29:00,058 --> 00:29:02,538
for a better life.

601
00:29:02,738 --> 00:29:04,538
You still think you have a reason?

602
00:29:14,699 --> 00:29:15,219
Forget it.

603
00:29:17,098 --> 00:29:17,899
Whatever.

604
00:29:19,379 --> 00:29:19,979
It's over.

605
00:29:23,098 --> 00:29:23,699
Listen,

606
00:29:24,899 --> 00:29:26,859
if you weren't Ms. Li's boyfriend,

607
00:29:29,098 --> 00:29:30,419
I'd have beaten you senseless!

608
00:29:33,018 --> 00:29:33,738
Do it.

609
00:29:36,498 --> 00:29:37,379
She and I

610
00:29:38,738 --> 00:29:39,238
broke up.

611
00:29:45,619 --> 00:29:46,338
What?

612
00:29:47,379 --> 00:29:51,219
Didn't I just approve
your marriage application?

613
00:29:51,738 --> 00:29:52,498
Are you serious?

614
00:29:54,699 --> 00:29:55,258
In life,

615
00:29:56,419 --> 00:29:57,659
you must learn to choose.

616
00:30:07,619 --> 00:30:08,619
So, you mean

617
00:30:10,578 --> 00:30:12,139
you chose your career

618
00:30:13,538 --> 00:30:15,939
over Ms. Li and Yuehai?

619
00:30:27,419 --> 00:30:28,738
I'm killing you!

620
00:30:28,738 --> 00:30:30,419
Hit me! Right here! Do it!

621
00:30:32,379 --> 00:30:34,899
As a cadre, I can't hit anyone.

622
00:30:35,338 --> 00:30:38,338
But you're not human!

623
00:30:39,219 --> 00:30:40,379
I'm killing you!

624
00:30:41,738 --> 00:30:43,219
I'm killing you!

625
00:30:43,338 --> 00:30:43,979
Stop it!

626
00:30:44,219 --> 00:30:45,699
I'll compensate you.

627
00:30:48,098 --> 00:30:49,578
I'm beating you to death!

628
00:30:51,018 --> 00:30:51,818
(A few days later,)

629
00:30:52,498 --> 00:30:55,338
(Du Tao got internal disciplinary action
because of that article.)

630
00:30:56,459 --> 00:30:57,979
(Later, I heard he resigned.)

631
00:30:58,699 --> 00:31:00,258
(We never saw each other again.)

632
00:31:03,219 --> 00:31:04,459
I'm back!

633
00:31:04,538 --> 00:31:05,058
Mr. Zheng!

634
00:31:05,058 --> 00:31:05,859
I'm back!

635
00:31:06,699 --> 00:31:07,498
I'm back.

636
00:31:07,498 --> 00:31:07,998
I'm back!

637
00:31:08,578 --> 00:31:09,078
Mr. Zheng.

638
00:31:09,179 --> 00:31:09,699
Hello.

639
00:31:10,139 --> 00:31:10,818
How's business?

640
00:31:10,818 --> 00:31:11,379
Good.

641
00:31:11,498 --> 00:31:12,498
That's good.

642
00:31:12,979 --> 00:31:13,778
I'm back!

643
00:31:14,859 --> 00:31:15,859
How are you?

644
00:31:15,859 --> 00:31:16,359
I'm fine.

645
00:31:16,498 --> 00:31:17,338
That's good.

646
00:31:17,899 --> 00:31:18,939
Take care.

647
00:31:19,338 --> 00:31:19,838
Okay.

648
00:31:20,538 --> 00:31:21,659
If you need help, tell me.

649
00:31:21,659 --> 00:31:22,738
You're finally back!

650
00:31:23,139 --> 00:31:23,659
I'm back.

651
00:31:23,859 --> 00:31:25,018
Will you leave again?

652
00:31:25,338 --> 00:31:26,018
No, I won't.

653
00:31:26,318 --> 00:31:26,818
Great.

654
00:31:26,818 --> 00:31:27,578
Be steady.

655
00:31:27,778 --> 00:31:28,278
Alright.

656
00:31:28,298 --> 00:31:29,179
Work hard.

657
00:31:29,459 --> 00:31:30,899
Mr. Zheng, you're back.

658
00:31:30,919 --> 00:31:31,419
Sure.

659
00:31:31,419 --> 00:31:33,018
We're so happy you're back.

660
00:31:33,379 --> 00:31:35,058
Look, Mr. Zheng is back!

661
00:31:35,258 --> 00:31:36,939
Mr. Zheng is back!

662
00:31:37,659 --> 00:31:38,859
If you need anything,

663
00:31:38,939 --> 00:31:39,659
just let me know.

664
00:31:40,258 --> 00:31:40,899
I knew it!

665
00:31:41,058 --> 00:31:42,179
I knew you would be fine.

666
00:31:42,298 --> 00:31:43,018
I told them.

667
00:31:43,179 --> 00:31:45,179
I told you all! Look, Mr. Zheng is back!

668
00:31:45,379 --> 00:31:46,258
Isn't he back?

669
00:31:46,419 --> 00:31:47,058
Didn't I say so?

670
00:31:47,379 --> 00:31:48,818
- I've been learning idioms.
- Good.

671
00:31:49,498 --> 00:31:50,379
I've been learning.

672
00:31:50,379 --> 00:31:50,939
You're back.

673
00:31:51,018 --> 00:31:51,518
Yan.

674
00:31:51,738 --> 00:31:53,058
How's your business doing lately?

675
00:31:53,219 --> 00:31:54,738
Very good, thanks to you.

676
00:31:55,098 --> 00:31:55,859
See you.

677
00:31:56,498 --> 00:31:57,139
See you.

678
00:31:59,899 --> 00:32:02,738
Mr. Zheng is back!

679
00:32:30,674 --> 00:32:34,642
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

680
00:32:34,642 --> 00:32:37,938
♪And the dazed confusion♪

681
00:32:39,186 --> 00:32:41,891
♪Should we let go of♪

682
00:32:41,891 --> 00:32:44,114
♪The stubborn madness♪

683
00:32:44,578 --> 00:32:45,179
I'm back.

684
00:32:47,459 --> 00:32:48,498
Sorry to keep you waiting.

685
00:32:48,859 --> 00:32:51,139
I-I toured the entire town.

686
00:32:52,018 --> 00:32:53,098
Let everyone see me

687
00:32:53,659 --> 00:32:54,298
to assure them.

688
00:32:54,859 --> 00:32:55,738
I'm fine now.

689
00:32:58,498 --> 00:33:00,018
You all helped with the investigation?

690
00:33:01,139 --> 00:33:01,738
Thank you.

691
00:33:03,442 --> 00:33:05,778
♪Who can still remember♪

692
00:33:05,778 --> 00:33:07,098
W-Why isn't anyone speaking?

693
00:33:08,498 --> 00:33:10,738
Little Conch, I brought you a gift.

694
00:33:12,379 --> 00:33:14,219
I got this from the guesthouse.

695
00:33:15,058 --> 00:33:15,558
Take it.

696
00:33:17,202 --> 00:33:19,922
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

697
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:24,504
♪Piercing the sorrow within♪

698
00:33:45,522 --> 00:33:48,699
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

699
00:33:48,699 --> 00:33:50,379
I just really missed you all.

700
00:33:51,859 --> 00:33:53,139
I'm really fine.

701
00:33:53,179 --> 00:33:54,139
I even gained weight.

702
00:33:54,298 --> 00:33:55,258
You can tell.

703
00:33:56,419 --> 00:33:57,098
Stop pinching me.

704
00:33:58,258 --> 00:33:58,758
Xie.

705
00:33:59,179 --> 00:34:00,659
You keep pinching me!

706
00:34:01,538 --> 00:34:03,139
You also got fat?
You have a round belly.

707
00:34:23,098 --> 00:34:23,779
Ms. Li,

708
00:34:25,779 --> 00:34:27,819
I just heard from people on the street.

709
00:34:28,538 --> 00:34:31,058
Thank you for taking care of them
during my absence.

710
00:34:32,618 --> 00:34:34,779
Mr. Zheng, you're finally back.

711
00:34:37,459 --> 00:34:40,098
I can finally return Yuehai to you.

712
00:34:45,739 --> 00:34:46,259
What's wrong?

713
00:34:46,698 --> 00:34:48,498
Mr. Zheng, my back hurts.

714
00:34:49,138 --> 00:34:49,939
What's wrong?

715
00:34:49,979 --> 00:34:50,578
What's wrong?

716
00:34:50,739 --> 00:34:51,339
A back problem?

717
00:34:55,339 --> 00:34:56,379
This really is my fault.

718
00:34:56,379 --> 00:34:57,939
It's not your fault, Mr. Zheng.

719
00:34:57,939 --> 00:34:59,218
You have to take responsibility.

720
00:34:59,218 --> 00:34:59,718
Doctor.

721
00:35:00,979 --> 00:35:03,658
Dr. Jiang, what exactly happened?

722
00:35:03,819 --> 00:35:04,979
How do you feel now?

723
00:35:05,939 --> 00:35:07,939
It's just painful.

724
00:35:08,058 --> 00:35:09,178
Don't move at all!

725
00:35:17,498 --> 00:35:18,779
Ms. Li, rest for a while.

726
00:35:19,618 --> 00:35:20,658
Okay. Don't move.

727
00:35:24,058 --> 00:35:25,118
The CT scan shows

728
00:35:25,218 --> 00:35:27,299
she has a lumbar disc protrusion.

729
00:35:27,779 --> 00:35:28,279
What?

730
00:35:29,498 --> 00:35:30,578
How so?

731
00:35:30,618 --> 00:35:32,819
I-I just hugged her once.

732
00:35:33,379 --> 00:35:35,259
Actually, during the investigation,

733
00:35:35,498 --> 00:35:36,419
I exercised a little.

734
00:35:36,618 --> 00:35:37,819
I didn't see this coming.

735
00:35:37,939 --> 00:35:39,459
Don't overstate your own strength.

736
00:35:40,618 --> 00:35:41,118
(Ward 06)
Look here.

737
00:35:43,018 --> 00:35:45,859
These two bones
are compressing the nerve.

738
00:35:46,138 --> 00:35:49,259
In theory, every step she takes
should be excruciatingly painful.

739
00:35:49,538 --> 00:35:51,779
I don't know how she's managed
to endure it until now.

740
00:35:55,419 --> 00:35:56,419
Is it very serious?

741
00:35:56,939 --> 00:35:57,939
So how do you treat her?

742
00:35:58,098 --> 00:36:00,618
We can't be sure yet.
We need to run a few more tests.

743
00:36:01,379 --> 00:36:03,218
According to the test results,

744
00:36:03,498 --> 00:36:05,698
we can determine
if surgery is necessary.

745
00:36:08,899 --> 00:36:09,618
She needs surgery?

746
00:36:09,939 --> 00:36:10,819
That is a possibility.

747
00:36:11,939 --> 00:36:12,439
Alright.

748
00:36:12,578 --> 00:36:14,618
You all shouldn't stay here.

749
00:36:15,419 --> 00:36:16,979
Just one person needs to stay for care.

750
00:36:17,459 --> 00:36:18,138
Who will it be?

751
00:36:18,739 --> 00:36:19,259
I will.

752
00:36:19,259 --> 00:36:20,178
- You.
- Yes.

753
00:36:20,178 --> 00:36:20,779
Be responsible.

754
00:36:21,158 --> 00:36:21,658
Sure.

755
00:36:21,658 --> 00:36:22,538
Well...

756
00:36:22,538 --> 00:36:23,299
I caused this.

757
00:36:23,339 --> 00:36:24,498
You're not suitable.

758
00:36:25,018 --> 00:36:26,058
I think you should stay.

759
00:36:26,658 --> 00:36:29,299
I'll have the nurse
give you specific instructions.

760
00:36:29,538 --> 00:36:30,038
Okay.

761
00:36:40,939 --> 00:36:41,618
Meng.

762
00:36:42,899 --> 00:36:43,979
I want some water.

763
00:36:44,578 --> 00:36:45,538
Okay.

764
00:36:47,859 --> 00:36:48,379
Dad.

765
00:36:49,618 --> 00:36:50,118
Qiuping.

766
00:36:50,339 --> 00:36:50,839
Mom.

767
00:36:51,939 --> 00:36:53,058
Don't move.

768
00:36:53,339 --> 00:36:54,379
What are you doing here?

769
00:36:55,859 --> 00:36:58,218
Mr. Zheng asked us to come.

770
00:37:03,819 --> 00:37:05,098
Why did he ask you to come here?

771
00:37:07,138 --> 00:37:07,939
What's wrong?

772
00:37:10,339 --> 00:37:11,739
Am I dying?

773
00:37:21,658 --> 00:37:22,939
Why are you crying?

774
00:37:23,698 --> 00:37:24,779
As we said,

775
00:37:25,098 --> 00:37:26,739
we won't cry in front of our daughter.

776
00:37:27,259 --> 00:37:28,098
I just feel

777
00:37:29,259 --> 00:37:31,578
we are terrible parents.

778
00:37:32,859 --> 00:37:35,218
Our child thinks we show up

779
00:37:35,658 --> 00:37:36,779
because she's dying.

780
00:37:43,459 --> 00:37:44,259
Stop crying.

781
00:37:44,698 --> 00:37:46,419
Aren't you usually calm?

782
00:37:46,779 --> 00:37:48,018
At this critical moment...

783
00:37:48,259 --> 00:37:49,299
Stop criticizing me again.

784
00:37:50,178 --> 00:37:51,259
Did you do better than me?

785
00:37:52,819 --> 00:37:54,419
That's more like it.

786
00:37:55,138 --> 00:37:57,299
You're better off being angry.

787
00:37:57,698 --> 00:37:59,739
Don't cry before our girl
these next few days.

788
00:38:08,379 --> 00:38:10,779
Don't forget the rules we made before.

789
00:38:12,018 --> 00:38:12,618
Okay.

790
00:38:13,618 --> 00:38:14,538
That's good.

791
00:38:15,859 --> 00:38:18,739
No arguing while our child is sick.

792
00:38:19,618 --> 00:38:20,899
Don't let her worry.

793
00:38:21,498 --> 00:38:23,819
Don't mention her breakup with Du Tao.

794
00:38:25,739 --> 00:38:28,138
If she doesn't bring that up,
we won't ask.

795
00:38:30,419 --> 00:38:30,939
Got it.

796
00:38:35,578 --> 00:38:36,098
Dr. Hou.

797
00:38:36,739 --> 00:38:37,259
Dr. Jiang.

798
00:38:37,538 --> 00:38:38,038
Go ahead.

799
00:38:38,138 --> 00:38:41,058
Now, you apply some spray for Ms. Li.

800
00:38:41,259 --> 00:38:42,618
I want to see how she recovers.

801
00:38:42,658 --> 00:38:46,018
Could you ask the nurse to guide her
through some rehabilitation exercises?

802
00:38:46,098 --> 00:38:46,598
Okay?

803
00:38:47,339 --> 00:38:47,839
Sure.

804
00:38:48,299 --> 00:38:48,799
Good.

805
00:38:49,578 --> 00:38:50,138
Ms. Yan.

806
00:38:51,218 --> 00:38:52,498
We just checked on Ms. Li.

807
00:38:53,939 --> 00:38:54,739
I'd like you

808
00:38:54,939 --> 00:38:55,578
- to meet...
- No need.

809
00:38:56,299 --> 00:38:56,939
Dr. Jiang,

810
00:38:57,498 --> 00:39:00,018
I'm Yan Jin, Qiuping's mother.

811
00:39:01,018 --> 00:39:03,299
Ms. Yan,
nice to meet you. I'm Jiang Yun.

812
00:39:05,498 --> 00:39:06,299
Unexpectedly,

813
00:39:09,538 --> 00:39:12,618
after all these years,
we've finally met.

814
00:39:14,739 --> 00:39:15,819
Am I bothering you?

815
00:39:17,018 --> 00:39:18,899
Sorry, I've been too busy.

816
00:39:19,218 --> 00:39:21,739
I should have gone
to Pingchuan to see you much sooner.

817
00:39:29,819 --> 00:39:32,339
Thank you for taking care of Qiuping.

818
00:39:32,739 --> 00:39:33,459
She really

819
00:39:34,779 --> 00:39:37,259
throws herself entirely into her work.

820
00:39:39,819 --> 00:39:42,618
So, while she's in the hospital,
I entrust her to your care.

821
00:39:43,259 --> 00:39:46,018
No problem. This is what I should do.

822
00:39:48,218 --> 00:39:49,098
Ms. Yan,

823
00:39:49,379 --> 00:39:52,259
Tao and Qiuping broke up.

824
00:39:52,819 --> 00:39:54,339
That's Tao's misfortune.

825
00:39:55,018 --> 00:39:57,578
I truly like Qiuping.

826
00:39:58,098 --> 00:39:59,178
But for her,

827
00:40:00,098 --> 00:40:01,299
it might not be a bad thing.

828
00:40:04,339 --> 00:40:05,058
Tao...

829
00:40:08,578 --> 00:40:09,578
It's just fate, I think.

830
00:40:10,939 --> 00:40:11,538
I have to go.

831
00:40:48,299 --> 00:40:48,939
Mom,

832
00:40:50,299 --> 00:40:51,299
do you and Dad know

833
00:40:51,698 --> 00:40:53,939
that Du Tao and I broke up?

834
